            <lg type="edition">
            <l>ñelikaḻai muḻaṅkaḻal vayamā verūuṅ</l>
            <l>kuṉṟuṭai yaruñcurañ celavayarn taṉaiyē</l>
            <l>naṉṟil koṇkaniṉ poruḷē</l>
            <l>pāvai yaṉṉaniṉ ṟuṇaippirintu varumē</l>                                       
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
              <l>You decided to go to the difficult desert full of hills,</l>
              <l></l>where tiger is frightened by the roaring fire [that sparked from] rubbing bamboos!
              <l></l>O man from the seashore! Your wealth isn’t good. 
              <l></l>After separating from your doll-like girl, do come back! 
              </lg>
